                            </a>
                        </div>
                        <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-body collapse">
                            <div class="accordion-inner">
                                This website can help you out: 
                                <a href=" https://accounts.google.com/SignUp?service=cl&continue=https%3A%2F%2Faccounts.google.com%2FManageAccount
 ">Link your account with Google </a>

