                            <div class="accordion-inner">
                                An awesome tip is to use  the following Chrome Extensions. Save and copy-paste the files in the correct Bohr folder in Google Drive
                                <ul><a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/save-to-google-drive/gmbmikajjgmnabiglmofipeabaddhgne?hl=en">Save to Google Drive </a></ul>
                                .
