Contact us if you want to become an ambassador: awesome@bohr.ac Thank you!

                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-group">
                        <div class="accordion-heading">
                            <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion2" href="#collapseSix">How awesome am I?
                            </a>
                        </div>
                        <div id="collapseSix" class="accordion-body collapse">
                            <div class="accordion-inner">
                                Since you use Bohr, you must be awesome. I mean like rockstar bling bling awesome! But seriously, thank you for using Bohr!
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>   
            </div>     
        </div>        
    </div>
</div>
